msgid "The portal immediately shows your dossier reference:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:67
msgid ""
"**No decision is returned at this point.** The process is now waiting for "
"caseworker review. You can track the status under **Mijn aanvragen**."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:74
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Application list status\" The list currently shows both completed "
"and open applications. No distinction has yet been made between the shell "
"process and its subprocess (**AwbShellProcess** and "
"**TreeFellingPermitSubProcess**)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:77
msgid "What happens in the background"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:79
msgid ""
"The AWB shell process runs automatically through phases 1–3 before pausing "
"at the first user task:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:81
msgid ""
"**Phase 1** — Identity script sets `applicantId`, `productType`, "
"`applicationDate`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:82
msgid ""
"**Phase 2** — Receipt script sets `receiptDate`, `awbDeadlineDate` (8 weeks, "
"Awb 4:13), `dossierReference`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:83
msgid ""
"**Phase 3** — `AwbCompletenessCheck` DMN evaluates whether the application "
"is complete (Awb 4:5)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:84
msgid "**Call Activity** — `TreeFellingPermitSubProcess` starts:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:84
msgid ""
"`TreeFellingDecision` DMN evaluates `treeDiameter` and `protectedArea` → "
"`permitDecision`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:84
msgid ""
"`ReplacementTreeDecision` DMN evaluates whether a replacement tree is "
"required → `replacementDecision`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:84
msgid "A `Sub_CaseReview` user task is created for caseworker review"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:88
msgid "**Process suspends** — awaiting caseworker action"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:90
msgid ""
"After the caseworker completes the review and confirms citizen notification "
"(`Task_Phase6_Notify`), the process ends and the final decision variables "
"are stored."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:92
msgid "Viewing the decision"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:94
msgid ""
"Once the caseworker completes both tasks and the process ends, a **Bekijk "
"beslissing** toggle appears on the application card in **Mijn aanvragen**. "
"Clicking the toggle expands the **Decision Viewer** panel below the card."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:96
msgid ""
"From v2.3.0, the Decision Viewer renders the official **decision letter** "
"authored in the [LDE Document Composer]{1} and bundled with the deployed "
"process. The letter includes the municipality letterhead, contact "
"information, dossier reference, the substantive decision text, and — if "
"applicable — replacement tree requirements. Variable placeholders in the "
"template are resolved from the final process variables automatically."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:103
msgid ""
"For applications submitted before document templates were introduced, the "
"viewer falls back to a compact readonly summary of the key decision fields."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:110
